name: Kthoomplayground
tagline: An initial playground for Kthoom, an online CBR, CBZ, and CBT extractor.
body:
# KthoomPlayground

This is me just playing around in Kthoom, a Comic book reader based on WebSlinger, but with added CBR and CBT extraction.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
